{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-detail-tsx","path":"/detail/06764d24-3040-57e0-ba49-62f6f1bfd4d3","result":{"pageContext":{"html":"<h1>CSP(Content-Security-Policy)</h1>\n<h2>大纲</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>基本概念</li>\n<li>目前 CSP 的使用情况</li>\n<li>一些具体场景下 CSP 的应用</li>\n<li>小结</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>基本概念</h2>\n<p>CSP 的全称是<code>Content-Security-Policy</code><sup><a href=\"#reference-1\">[1]</a></sup> ，是一种计算机安全标准，可以防御跨站脚本、点击劫持等代码注入攻击，阻止恶意内容在守信网页内容中执行。站点可以指定用户代理资源加载的策略，主要是通过响应头<code>Content-Security-Policy</code>，或者是使用带有<code>http-equiv</code>属性的 meta 标签来进行配置的。这可以有效的避免 xss 等一些代码注入形式的攻击。</p>\n<p>⚠️ 同时值得注意的是，部分属性并不能通过<code>meta</code>标签或者是响应头<code>Content-Security-Policy-Repory-Only</code>进行配置，需要将配置写到响应头<code>Content-Security-Policy</code>中。</p>\n<p>其基本的使用方式<sup><a href=\"#reference-2\">[2]</a></sup>为<code>Content-Secuirty-Policy: &#x3C;policy-directive>; [&#x3C;policy-directive>];</code> 通过设置指令对各类资源的加载，基本可以分为<code>获取指令</code>、<code>导航指令</code>、<code>报告指令</code>、<code>其他指令</code>。</p>\n<h3>获取指令(Fetch Directives)</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指令名</th>\n<th>主要作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>chlid-src</td>\n<td>限制了 worker 和 iframe 的资源来源</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>connect-src</td>\n<td>限制了通过脚本接口加载的链接的地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>default-src</td>\n<td>作为其他<code>获取指令</code>的备选项</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>font-src</td>\n<td>限制了<code>@font-face</code> 加载的源字体的地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>frame-src</td>\n<td>限制了 iframe 的加载源</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>script-src</td>\n<td>限制 JavaScript 的源地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>style-src</td>\n<td>限制层叠样式表的源地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>...</td>\n<td>...</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><code>script-src</code><sup><a href=\"#reference-3\">[3]</a></sup>是比较常见的指令，我们可以从主机名、协议名、是否与当前文档同源、是否允许各种形式的 eval、是否允许内联的 event handlers、是否允许内联的 script 标签或者是 javascript 伪协议的链接等这样一些方面对文档中使用的 javascript 代码进行管理。同时我们也可以使用<code>nonce</code>或者是<code>代码文本hash值</code>这样一些方式对代码的合法性进行验证，避免在开启<code>unsafe-inline</code>时，非法的&#x3C;script>代码段被执行。</p>\n<h3>文档指令(Document Directives)</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指令名</th>\n<th>主要作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>sandbox</td>\n<td>类似于 iframe 的 sandbox 属性，约束 iframe 中的行为</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>...</td>\n<td>...</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>导航指令(Navigation Directives)</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指令名</th>\n<th>主要作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>from-action</td>\n<td>限制 form 表单的 action 属性</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>frame-ancestor</td>\n<td>限制资源被以 iframe、frame、object、embed 等形式嵌入时的有效的父级元素</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>...</td>\n<td>...</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>报告指令</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指令名</th>\n<th>主要作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>report-uri</td>\n<td>需要配合<code>Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only</code>使用，对可能发生 XSS 的违规行为进行上报</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>目前 CSP 的使用情况</h2>\n<p>观察了<code>zhihu.com</code>、<code>taobao.com</code>、<code>douban.com</code>、<code>juejin.com</code>，目前只有<code>zhihu.com</code>使用 CSP 保护。</p>\n<h3>知乎(zhihu.com)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/08037/csp_implement_zhihu.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.972972972972975%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"csp-implement-zhihu\"\n        title=\"csp-implement-zhihu\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/fcda8/csp_implement_zhihu.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/12f09/csp_implement_zhihu.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/e4a3f/csp_implement_zhihu.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/fcda8/csp_implement_zhihu.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/efc66/csp_implement_zhihu.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/c83ae/csp_implement_zhihu.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e24a8ab26ba4334c9cf464fcda442a85/08037/csp_implement_zhihu.png 1379w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div align=\"center\" ><small>图1 - zhihu.com</small></div>\n可以观察到zhihu.com对`img-src`、`connect-src`、`script-src`、`style-src`都做了配置。\n<h2>一些具体场景下 CSP 的应用</h2>\n<h3>进一步避免 XSS 攻击</h3>\n<p>CSP 可以作为一个更安全的防止 XSS 的策略。</p>\n<p>从 XSS 攻击的目的讲，XSS 主要是为了窃取用户的 cookie 或者其他数据，又或者是通过 js 代码的执行使用户代理发起意料之外的请求，又或者是在用户网页中生成动态内容。对于前者我们可以通过 cookie 的<code>httpOnly</code>属性避免 js 对该 cookie 进行读写，对于第二种情况，也就是 CSRF 的一种攻击形式，常见的解决方案是检查 reference、检查请求的 token 等。对于这种 CSRF 的场景，前面的方案都是从服务端做检查，除了 CSP 还没有比较好的在用户代理就进行检查的解决方案，虽然说使用<code>service worker</code>可以对资源请求进行拦截，但是使用这个方案防止 CSRF 确实不太合适。对于第二、第三种情况，使用 CSP 就可以很好的解决，可以分别对文档的<code>connect-src</code>和<code>script-src</code>作出约束，浏览器借此判断出非法的 ajax 请求的连接和非法来源的 js 代码。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// app.js</span>\napp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">use</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"Content-Security-Policy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"connect-src 'self';script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>对 script-src 进行拦截</h4>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/27f8b/csp_implement_enhance1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 34.45945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement enhance1\" title=\"csp implement enhance1\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance1.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/12f09/csp_implement_enhance1.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/e4a3f/csp_implement_enhance1.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance1.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/efc66/csp_implement_enhance1.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/c83ae/csp_implement_enhance1.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0f5ee1297e769430ad63ba9773844724/27f8b/csp_implement_enhance1.png 1730w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/b8bf8/csp_implement_enhance2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 39.86486486486486%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement enhance2\" title=\"csp implement enhance2\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance2.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/12f09/csp_implement_enhance2.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/e4a3f/csp_implement_enhance2.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance2.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/efc66/csp_implement_enhance2.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/c83ae/csp_implement_enhance2.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c7402fddb439bd9f46584ea5ef1bbb5d/b8bf8/csp_implement_enhance2.png 1728w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>⚠️ 需要注意的是，如果原来的站点使用了 JSONP 解决跨域，需要将 JSONP 对应的域名加入<code>script-src</code>中。虽然 script 标签不受同源策略限制，但是 CSP 可能会对 script 的来源进行限制。</p>\n<h4>对 connect-src 进行拦截</h4>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/6c86f/csp_implement_enhance3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 40.54054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement enhance3\" title=\"csp implement enhance3\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance3.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/12f09/csp_implement_enhance3.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/e4a3f/csp_implement_enhance3.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance3.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/efc66/csp_implement_enhance3.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/c83ae/csp_implement_enhance3.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1ffda4ef410e1bd4dc213e216b7861ef/6c86f/csp_implement_enhance3.png 1720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/9685e/csp_implement_enhance4.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.4054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement enhance4\" title=\"csp implement enhance4\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance4.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/12f09/csp_implement_enhance4.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/e4a3f/csp_implement_enhance4.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/fcda8/csp_implement_enhance4.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/efc66/csp_implement_enhance4.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/c83ae/csp_implement_enhance4.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2fc5c5f5ea6598ae736efee18e5b7e1f/9685e/csp_implement_enhance4.png 1336w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>相比的跨域拦截，CSP 的<code>connect-src</code>对请求的拦截，不存在需要类似跨域请求预检的过程。即使接口地址允许跨域，也可以将请求拦截下来，更好地避免 CSRF 攻击。</p>\n<h3>避免运营商的 HTTP 劫持</h3>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 418px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1f29d477c554ff777a5befe45a800357/d7398/csp_implemnt_isp-hijack.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 179.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implemnt isp hijack\" title=\"csp implemnt isp hijack\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1f29d477c554ff777a5befe45a800357/d7398/csp_implemnt_isp-hijack.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1f29d477c554ff777a5befe45a800357/12f09/csp_implemnt_isp-hijack.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1f29d477c554ff777a5befe45a800357/e4a3f/csp_implemnt_isp-hijack.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1f29d477c554ff777a5befe45a800357/d7398/csp_implemnt_isp-hijack.png 418w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 418px) 100vw, 418px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<div align=\"center\" ><small>图2 - 运营商劫持</small></div>\n上图为运营商HTTP劫持插入广告的效果<sup>[[4]](#reference-4)</sup>。其基本形式就是通过在文档末尾添加一些js代码，通过执行这些代码，在页面中动态添加广告位并诱导用户点击广告链接。CSP就可以作为一个有力的措施避免这种行为。对于图中的场景可以使用`navigate-to` （目前navigate-to仍是处于Working Draft阶段）防止用户跳转至广告页面、限制`img-src`避免广告图片被加载、限制`script-src`避免这段插入的js文件被加载。\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">use</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"Content-Security-Policy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"navigation-to 'self';img-src *;script-src 'self' nonce-2726c7f26c \"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/e2cbf/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 26.351351351351354%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement isp hijack1\" title=\"csp implement isp hijack1\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/fcda8/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/12f09/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/e4a3f/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/fcda8/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/efc66/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/c83ae/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/44775d3495bf14dcbbc61c88c8722e3b/e2cbf/csp_implement_isp-hijack1.png 2138w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/874d1/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 79.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement isp hijack2\" title=\"csp implement isp hijack2\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/fcda8/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/12f09/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/e4a3f/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/fcda8/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/efc66/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/c83ae/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/574aeb58ffc887455ef54bb3c6ce4102/874d1/csp_implement_isp-hijack2.png 1310w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>对于这种场景，CSP 可以做到在执行 script 脚本这一步，就将该行为阻止。</p>\n<h3>防止网页被他人以 iframe 的形式盗用</h3>\n<p>网页可以通过 iframe 的方式嵌入到另一个网页中。但是对于被嵌入的网页来说，这并不一定是意料之中的。为了避免这种情况，可以设置被嵌入页面的<code>frame-ancestors</code>来进行限制。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">use</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Content-Security-Policy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"frame-ancestors 'none'\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/b8471/csp_implement_iframe.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 29.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"csp implement iframe\" title=\"csp implement iframe\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/fcda8/csp_implement_iframe.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/12f09/csp_implement_iframe.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/e4a3f/csp_implement_iframe.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/fcda8/csp_implement_iframe.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/efc66/csp_implement_iframe.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/c83ae/csp_implement_iframe.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6a4d261baee67d27eac151f64ab52cd9/b8471/csp_implement_iframe.png 2016w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h3>XSS 攻击的拦截上报</h3>\n<p>对于 XSS 攻击我们除了要做有事前的防范，还要有事后的补救，如何将这个攻击过程记录下来，更好地交给安全人员去复现去分析？如何以各种方式通知用户，当前的账户可能存在安全风险，需要及时更换密码？等等。使用<code>report-uri</code> 这个属性<sup><a href=\"#reference-5\">[5]</a>(</sup>，可以告知浏览器将违反报告发送到指定的 URI。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> router <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Router</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nrouter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/report\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">ctx</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"report comes\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\napp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">use</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">routes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\napp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">use</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Content-Security-Policy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"img-src 'self';report-uri /report\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/317ed534f4faac1d0591b6